title: Giadas Holiday Handbook S01E06 Kids Gingerbread House Party PDTV
description:
Giada's Holiday Handbook - Season 1, Episode 6




Kids' Gingerbread House Party

Giada De Laurentiis treats her daughter, Jade, and her friends to a fun-filled party where they each make their own unique gingerbread house. She serves fun kids' treats like S'more Popcorn, Pizza Grilled Cheese, Veggie Forest with Parmesan Ranch Dip and Frozen Hot Chocolate Affogatos.




Original Air Date: 13-Dec-2015
